<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>cadu-leite - blog</title><link>http://cadu-leite.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="http://cadu-leite.github.io/rss/css.rss.xml" rel="self"></atom:link><lastBuildDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2014 00:00:00 -0300</lastBuildDate><item><title>Compilando Bootstrap Twitter V3 Less no Ubuntu</title><link>http://cadu-leite.github.io/posts/2014/Mar/04/compilando-bootstrap-twitter-ubuntu/</link><description>&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Atualizar o node e o less, o que vem do repositório é antigo e não compila. por via das dúvidas ...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;update&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;python&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;software&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;properties&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;python&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;g&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;++&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;make&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;add&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;repository&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;ppa&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;chris&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;lea&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;node&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;js&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;update&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;nodejs&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;autoremove&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;node&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;less&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;npm&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;g&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;less&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;fonte: &lt;a href="http://edmondscommerce.github.io/less%20css/compiling-twitter-bootstraps-less-files-on-ubuntu-12-04mint-13.html" title="passo-a-passo para instalar lessc atualizado no ubuntu"&gt;lessc atualizado no ubuntu&lt;/a&gt; e &lt;a href="http://askubuntu.com/questions/272780/ubuntu-12-10-lessc-1-3-3-installation"&gt;ubuntu-12-10-lessc-1-3-3-installation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Baixe o  o código LESS do &lt;a href="https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/" title="repositório do Booststrap-twitter "&gt;Bootstrap-twitter&lt;/a&gt;, não o css compilado do site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;O códifo &lt;em&gt;fonte&lt;/em&gt; do bootstrap twitter é um conjunto de arquivos &lt;strong&gt;less&lt;/strong&gt;, o arquivo principal a ser compilado é o &lt;code&gt;bootstrap.less&lt;/code&gt; . Este arquivo importa todos os outros arquivos.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Adicione suas customizações.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;eu preferi manter a o código original sem alterá-lo, e adicionei um arquivo &lt;code&gt;theme_1.less&lt;/code&gt; com minhas alterações, para que fosse compilado junto . Adicionei este arquivo ao final dos &lt;em&gt;imports&lt;/em&gt; no arquivo  &lt;code&gt;bootstrap.less&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Utility classes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="cp"&gt;@import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;utilities.less&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="cp"&gt;@import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;responsive-utilities.less&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="cp"&gt;@import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;custom.less&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="c1"&gt;// &amp;lt;&amp;lt; CUSTOMIZAÇÃO DO LESS&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bash script para gerar um arquivo &lt;code&gt;.css&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Para testar minhas modificações mantive um bash script re-compilando o less a medida que o alterava, e gerando um arquivo &lt;code&gt;.css&lt;/code&gt; que visualizava em um template &lt;code&gt;.html&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table class="highlighttable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="linenos"&gt;&lt;div class="linenodiv"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;1
2
3
4
5
6
7&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class="code"&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="c"&gt;#!/bin/bash&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="o"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;$2&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;||&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;Specify both .less and .css files&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;exit &lt;/span&gt;1; &lt;span class="o"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
inotifywait -m -e close_write . | &lt;span class="k"&gt;while &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;read &lt;/span&gt;x op f; &lt;span class="k"&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="k"&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;$f&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;span class="nb"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;Change detected. Recompiling...&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
    lessc &lt;span class="nv"&gt;$2&lt;/span&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;span class="nv"&gt;$3&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;quot;`date`: COMPILED&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;span class="k"&gt;done&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;fonte: a idéia deste script veio de um &lt;a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/13671969/how-to-automatically-compile-less-into-css-on-the-server/22104784#22104784" title="stack overflow sobre "&gt;post no stack overflow&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;para que o script funcione execute ...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;less_compile&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;sh&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;diretorio&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;monitorado&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="n"&gt;bootstrap&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;less&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;custom&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;bootstrap&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;css&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;! É importante gerar o custom.css &lt;strong&gt;fora&lt;/strong&gt; do path a ser monitorado, por motivos óbvios, do contrário o script bash entrará em um loop infinito de chamadas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Uma dica após terminar a customização é utilizar o &lt;a href="https://github.com/GoalSmashers/clean-css" title="css formater"&gt;clean-css&lt;/a&gt; - um aplicativo node.js que minifica, formata entre outras opções  o arquivo css gerado.&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Cadu-leite</dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2014 00:00:00 -0300</pubDate><guid>tag:cadu-leite.github.io,2014-03-04:posts/2014/Mar/04/compilando-bootstrap-twitter-ubuntu/</guid><category>web-design</category><category>less</category><category>css</category></item></channel></rss>